        {
            "title": "法國總統馬克龍支持貝魯舉行信任投票 排除辭職可能性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"870\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4h3uihjvMepHiBgQ5uIjcg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg3MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/234c494aadbd97be485a7505651ef164\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國總統埃馬紐埃爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬克龍;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬克龍\">馬克龍</a>重申，支持總理弗朗索瓦·貝魯要求議會9月8日舉行信任投票的決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克龍拒絕討論如果貝魯政府因為未通過信任投票而倒台，他會做出何種選擇。可能的選項包括任命新總理或解散國民議會並舉行提前選舉。但馬克龍堅稱他不會辭職，儘管一些政黨要求他這麼做。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「是法國人民賦予我的使命，我將履行至任期結束，」馬克龍周五在與德國總理默茨共同舉行的記者會上說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝魯的下台將使馬克龍回到自去年提前選舉以來一直無法擺脫的僵局，即沒有明顯的候選人能夠在被三股對立陣營分裂的國民議會中推動立法通過。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括極右翼國民聯盟在內的反對黨敦促馬克龍再次冒險舉行新的立法選舉，甚至提前舉行總統選舉。但馬克龍一直抵制要求他在2027年任期結束前辭職的呼聲。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"870\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xfvd7uhpqMjoYni.zEAWRA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg3MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4877349753a0f8e8d2e655aca4d87c30\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Macron Backs Bayrou’s Confidence Motion, Rules Out Resigning (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%9D%E9%AD%AF%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-201522403.html",
